The Atheme SVN repository can be checked out using the following command:
	svn co http://svn.atheme.org/atheme/trunk atheme-current

The stable version can be checked out using the following command:
	svn co http://svn.atheme.org/atheme/branches/release-1.0 atheme-stable

Atheme's SVN repository can be browsed over the internet at the 
following address:
	http://viewsvn.atheme.org/
